                                <span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;">When available on our platform, currency conversion features are provided for guidance only, and such conversions are not real-time.&nbsp; Prices may be displayed in various currencies for your convenience.&nbsp; However, the final charge will be processed in the specified transaction currency.&nbsp; Exchange rates are determined by our banking partners and may fluctuate.&nbsp; We are not responsible for any additional charges imposed by your payment providers.</span>
